name: Sitting Pussy Position
description:
Hello! This LORA is responsible for making a certain position quite reliably.

Since we all know that hands and feet are not really SDs forte, the training data was set up to alleviate that problem.

As a result - you should be getting nice results pretty much every time.

The trigger is the keyphrase "pstng position", for example: "woman in pstng position" is enough to generate some nice content.

This LORA works on various models. Hovewer I have not tested yet on anime ones, but seeing how flexible it is (skin color, etc) I see no reason why it would not work.

There are two LORAs, with lower and higher precision (differs in size), but the training was all the same.

PS. I have a DB model of this as well, if someone is interested - just let me know and I can make it available if needed!
